thread.title: Ben & Emma
thread.title_full: Nelson Alexander reviewed by Ben & Emma

author: Ben & Emma
title: Ben & Emma
text: We were very happy with Nelson Alexander when they sold our apartment. Luke and Monique were great. We were particularly impressed by Monique who was extremely helpful in directing us to people who were able to help prepare our home for sale. She was also excellent at communication and very prompt. Thanks for a great sale!
